{
  "texts": [
    "We have experimentally evaluated and compared the EPS of the SIEM systems which have already been explained in detail in Section 5.",
    "The core purpose of a SIEM system is to detect events using correlation rules.",
    "Some SIEM solutions have rudimentary correlation rules while others have a more advanced and robust set of rules.",
    "We perform a quantitative as well as qualitative analysis of the correlation rules of each SIEM solution.",
    "Every SIEM system comes with built-in correlation rules."
  ]
}